Comment: 0,0:02:59.03,0:02:59.07,op jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:05.00,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}This is a fate that brought us here watch my long shot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:15.56,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Feel like I am falling into the flame of lies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:18.20,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Tell me what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:22.60,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Trying not to step back to where I used to belong
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.46,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Looking for the escape from pain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:29.86,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I will cross my fingers hoping not to be sacrificed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:33.30,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}約束したんだ君とその希望に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:37.06,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Get in the raid Get ready for the time to come
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:40.60,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}浮かび上がるシルエット追いかけ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:43.96,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Drop down the reason why I'm standing here alone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:47.53,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}May be it's already too late to regain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:52.90,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}運命としてかかげた灯を失くさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:54.23,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Ever again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:57.70,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}What if I could right my wrongs and save you from the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.46,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}It's not enough
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:07.20,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}It's not enough for me to break the rule upon this world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:12.23,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I will never gonna leave you never wanna lose you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.56,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}we'll make it in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:20.86,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Not backing down for real I won't trace someone else's life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:23.23,op jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I know who I am
Comment: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:10.99,op ch,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:05.00,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}命运将我们引领至此 并看着我跳战不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:15.56,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}感觉我堕入了谎言的火焰中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:18.20,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}说出你对我的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:22.60,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}尽力不去走回头路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.46,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}探求走出痛苦的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:29.86,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我合十双手去祈求不必牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:33.30,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}这是我和你的希望所订下的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:37.06,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}在时机成熟前做好出击的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:40.60,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}去追赶那个浮现出来的黑影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:43.96,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}放弃那个让我单独一人的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:47.53,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}或许这已经太迟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:52.90,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不要舍去作为命运的那道光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:54.23,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}没有下次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:57.70,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}若我能修补错误并将你救出苦海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.46,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}这并不足以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:07.20,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}并不足以让我打破这世界的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:12.23,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我绝不离开你 绝不想失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.56,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我们来结束这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:20.86,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}别再退缩 这辈子我不会跟随别人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:23.23,op ch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我知道自己是谁
